<p>In fact, for demonstrative purposes, in the above paragraph, I used 'linebreaks' instead of spaces:<img src="https://i.stack.imgur.com/3pCqU.png" alt="enter image description here"></p>

<p>I realise I can use <code>&lt;br /&gt;</code> to add line breaks, but this soon becomes cumbersome.</p>

<p>Might I request that:</p>

